nuns were killed at Busasamana. The five were buried at Nyundo,
near Gisenyi today, the conference indicated.
</P>
<P>
It has not been possible to confirm the exact number of nuns
who were murdered at Busasamana.
</P>
<P>
Two other clergy people, a Belgian nun and a Canadian priest,
were killed in north-western Rwanda last year in attacks blamed
on Hutu extremists. 
