militants seeking to oust Mubarak and install a purist Islamic
state in Egypt. It has also charged Khartoum with sheltering
gunmen who tried to assassinate Mubarak in 1995.
</P>
<P>
Sudan denied the charges and criticized Egypt for letting
Sudan's opposition in exile operate from Cairo.
</P>
