He asked customs officers to do an even better job this year,
when both domestic and international economies are having some
changes.
</P>
<P>
An effort should be made to integrate Chinese customs with
advanced countries to meet the development needs of a socialist
market economy, Li said, and asked customs officers to improve
their political and professional qualifications and ethical
standards. 
