and collective organization losses, sources say.
</P>
<P>
Shenzhen's procuratorates worked hard to investigate cases of
bribing officials and abuse of power while in office.
</P>
<P>
Some 160 cases were serious ones involving 170 people, of whom
12 were officials suspected of taking bribes worth one to five
million yuan each.
</P>
<P>
Procuratorates in Shenzhen have stepped up their campaign to
combat crimes to maintain social order.  
