with increased bilateral economic and trade cooperation, said
Almunia. he expressed his belief that the links and cooperation
between the two parties and two countries would be reinforced.
</P>
<P>
Jiang also briefed the Spanish visitors on China's reform and
opening up.
</P>
<P>
The Spanish visitors are here at the invitation of the CPC.
