<HEADLINE> Myanmar to Conduct Census on Human Resources </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
YANGON, January 13 (Xinhua) -- Myanmar is planning to carry out
a census on human resources in order to promote economic
development, the official newspaper The New Light of Myanmar
reported Tuesday.
</P>
