<HEADLINE> Results of FIFA World Player of Year Award </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
PARIS, January 12 (Xinhua) -- Following are the result of the
FIFA world player of the year award made here on Monday (tabulated
under name, country, club and points):
</P>
<P>
1. Ronaldo, Brazil, Inter Milan, 480 points
</P>
<P>
2. Roberto Carlos, Brazil, Real Madrid, 65
</P>
<P>
3. Dennis Bergkamp, Netherlands, Arsenal, 62
</P>
<P>
Zinedine Zidane, France, Juventus, 62
</P>
<P>
5. Raul, Spain, Real Madrid, 51
